*Ponovio* je isti stav više puta. (He repeated the same opinion multiple times.)

Nije bilo dovoljno vremena da *ponovim* predavanje. (There wasn't enough time to repeat the lecture.)

Ona je *ponovila* svoj odgovor. (She repeated her answer.)

Oni nisu uspeli da *ponove* uspeh prvog albuma. (They weren't able to repeat the success of the first album.)

Moraš da *ponoviš* još jednom. (You have to repeat again.)